  <brief_title>Mental Health Promotion Interventions Among Migrant Workers in China</brief_title>
  <official_title>Mental Health Promotion Interventions for Reducing Self-reported Depression and Improving Rates of Early Detection of Depression Among Migrant Workers in China, a Cluster Randomised Controlled Trial</official_title>
