  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goals of this research were to conduct a mental health intervention study for reducing
      self-reported depression and anxiety among migrant workers in a labor-intensive industry in
      China and to assess the effectiveness of the integrated mental health interventions aimed at
      promoting the mental health of migrant workers in labor-intensive industries in China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
